headline: NVIDIA, Dell fall after-hours after SMCI’s Q3 warning
summary: Investing.com - NVIDIA (NASDAQ:NVDA) shares fell 1.7% in after-hours trading on Tuesday after major customer Super Micro Computer Inc (NASDAQ:SMCI) issued preliminary third quarter results well below estimates. Super Micro makes advanced AI servers that include NVIDIA chips.
